counterPicks.name: Iron Fist
counterPicks.description: Iron Fist can get behind Ultron and pressure him mid-air, making him unable to support his allies.

counterPicks.name: Spider-Man
counterPicks.description: He can be a pain to deal in the air with his high mobility.

counterPicks.name: Namor
counterPicks.description: Namor's long-range attacks and spawns are effective counters to Ultron. Additionally, his Blessings of the Deep (Shift) allows him to reposition strategically, allowing him to attack Ultron from unexpected angles.

counterPicks.name: Star-Lord
counterPicks.description: He can chase and solo-kill Ultron in mid air almost instantly.

counterPicks.name: The Punisher
counterPicks.description: He can pressure Ultron while maintaining consistent damage output, and force him to retreat.

counterPicks.name: Psylocke
counterPicks.description: Her mobility and quick damage output can burst Ultron while he's busy supporting his allies.

counterPicks.name: Black Widow
counterPicks.description: Black Widow's mechanics as a sniper is a natural counter to Ultron as she can snipe him in a safe distance.

counterPicks.name: Hela
counterPicks.description: She can land massive damage to Ultron in a safe distance.

counterPicks.name: Hawkeye
counterPicks.description: Similar with Hela, he can land massive damage to Ultron in a safe distance.

counterPicks.name: Adam Warlock
counterPicks.description: Adam's attack damage and projectile speed as a strategist make him a hard counter to flying heroes like Ultron.
